title: Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in Canada 2019
summary: The graph shows the trend of the Total Number of Canadian vehicles returning to Canada during the year 2019 .
The Number drops between January and February shows the minimum value in February .
From February on it increases and shows the maximum value in August .
gold: This is a line chart that shows the trend of the total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in the year 2019 . The amount remains low during the winter months including January to March and October to December . There 's an increasing trend starting from March to August when it reaches the highest point .
